    "Name": "Erebus",
    "Details": "The P1 variant of the Erebus mounts a Large Improved Heavy Laser in each arm besides the Prototype Mass Driver. Being the first prototype in the line of the chassis, it still is considered one of the better. The main weakness, like all the other models, is the low weapons count.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.4</color></b>",
